017d\u00e1k |year=2016 |title=Applying the Weapon of Theory: Comparing the Philosophy of Julius Kambarage Nyerere and Kwame Nkrumah |journal=Journal of African Cultural Studies |volume=28 |issue=2 |pages=147\u2013160 |doi=10.1080/13696815.2015.1053798 |ref=}}\n\n{{Refend}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Sister project links|wikt=no|b=no|n=no|s=no|v=no|voy=no|species=no|d=Q186525|display=Julius Nyerere}}\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20060911223145/http://www.southcentre.org/mwalimu/ SouthCentre Nyerere Memorial Site]\n**[https://web.archive.org/web/20011225222030/http://www.southcentre.org/mwalimu/speeches/written/written.htm Mwalimu Neyerere Speeches]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20051120184754/http://www.anc.org.za/ancdocs/history/people/nyerere/newsart.html Nyerere Obituary] from the [[African National Congress]]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20061019131749/http://www.africasummit.org/about/nyererefellowship.html Julius Nyerere Fellowship]\n*[http://www.ed.ac.uk/schools-departments/student-funding/postgraduate/international/region/nyerere The Julius Nyerere Master's Scholarships (University of Edinburgh)]\n\n{{Navboxes\n|title=Offices and distinctions\n|list1=\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-ppo}}\n{{s-bef|before=Himself as Chairman of [[Tanganyika African National Union|<abbr title=\"Tanganyika African National Union\">TANU</abbr>]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=National Chairman of [[Chama Cha Mapinduzi]]|years=1977\u20131990}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Ali Hassan Mwinyi]]}}\n{{s-new|party}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Chairman of [[Tanganyika African National Union|<abbr title=\"Tanganyika African National Union\">TANU</abbr>]]|years=1954\u20131977}}\n{{s-aft|after=Himself as Chairman of [[Chama Cha Mapinduzi|CCM]]}}\n{{s-off}}\n{{s-bef|before=Himself (as [[President of Tanganyika]])<br />[[Abeid Karume]] (as [[President of Zanzibar]])}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[List of Presidents of Tanzania|President of Tanzania]]|years=1964\u20131985}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Ali Hassan Mwinyi]]}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Elizabeth II]] (as Quee